The paper deals with the problem of clustering high-dimensional data that evolves over time, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. The use of LSTM networks and self-expressive trait of the data suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data mining (cs.DM), and information theory (cs.IT).
